<div class="page-about pt-nav">

  {%- comment -%} ── 1. HERO ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="about-hero">
    {%- if section.settings.hero_image != blank -%}
      <img
        src="{{ section.settings.hero_image | image_url: width: 2400 }}"
        alt="the pretty fix — Our Story"
        class="about-hero__img"
        loading="eager"
      >
    {%- else -%}
      <div class="about-hero__placeholder">[ Photo: Wide lifestyle shot — product detail or brand visual ]</div>
    {%- endif -%}
    <div class="about-hero__overlay">
      <span class="about-eyebrow">Built to endure</span>
      <h1 class="about-hero__title">Our Story</h1>
      <p class="about-hero__sub">Built to last. Built for the long run.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} ── 2. THE ORIGIN ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-split">
        <div class="about-split__text">
          <span class="about-eyebrow about-eyebrow--dark">The idea</span>
          <h2 class="about-heading">She Tried Everything.<br>Nothing Stuck.</h2>
          <p class="about-body">She's 27. She has tech neck. She knows. Her chiropractor has mentioned it. Her phone caused it. She's not putting down her phone.</p>
          <p class="about-body">She's tried braces. Reminders. The 30-day yoga challenge for 5 days. The gym for 3 weeks. Willpower. None of it stuck — not because she's lazy, but because she's exhausted, and the methods were wrong.</p>
          <p class="about-body">So she said: enough. I'm not going to fix this with effort. I'm going to fix it the way I fix my skin — with something that works while I do nothing. That's where <em>the pretty fix</em> begins.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-split__media">
          {%- if section.settings.photo_patricio != blank -%}
            <img
              src="{{ section.settings.photo_patricio | image_url: width: 900 }}"
              alt="the pretty fix — The idea"
              class="about-split__img"
              loading="lazy"
            >
            <p class="about-caption">Rest is the work.</p>
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="about-photo-placeholder">
              <span>📷 Photo: Brand visual, lifestyle,<br>or hero product shot</span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 3. STATS BAR — our values ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-stats">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-stats__grid">
        <div class="about-stat">
          <span class="about-stat__num">01</span>
          <span class="about-stat__label">Passive</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat about-stat--divider">
          <span class="about-stat__num">02</span>
          <span class="about-stat__label">Permission</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat about-stat--divider">
          <span class="about-stat__num">03</span>
          <span class="about-stat__label">Pretty</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat about-stat--divider">
          <span class="about-stat__num">04</span>
          <span class="about-stat__label">Precision</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 4. WHAT WE STAND FOR ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--beige">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-split about-split--reverse">
        <div class="about-split__media">
          {%- if section.settings.photo_tannery != blank -%}
            <img
              src="{{ section.settings.photo_tannery | image_url: width: 900 }}"
              alt="the pretty fix — What we stand for"
              class="about-split__img"
              loading="lazy"
            >
            <p class="about-caption">Pretty fix. Real fix.</p>
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="about-photo-placeholder">
              <span>📷 Photo: Lifestyle, product in use,<br>or brand moment</span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
        <div class="about-split__text">
          <span class="about-eyebrow about-eyebrow--dark">What we stand for</span>
          <h2 class="about-heading">Pretty Without<br>Performing.</h2>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>Passive</strong> — every piece works while you live your actual life. No new routines, no new mornings, no new willpower.</p>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>Permission</strong> — rest is the work. Lazy is not a flaw. We don't sell hustle dressed up as wellness.</p>
          <blockquote class="about-quote">
            "I don't wanna lean in. I wanna lie down."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 5. HOW WE CURATE ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-split">
        <div class="about-split__text">
          <span class="about-eyebrow about-eyebrow--dark">How we built it</span>
          <h2 class="about-heading">Three Pieces.<br>One Passive Fix.</h2>
          <p class="about-body">We didn't want a catalog. We wanted the smallest possible system that would actually solve the problem. So we kept it to three pieces, plus the rituals around them.</p>
          <p class="about-body">The bra fixes posture by day. The sleep pillow resets it by night. The cream, the gua sha, the masks — those are the rituals. Every piece works without you having to try.</p>
          <p class="about-body">Developed with input from chiropractors and physical therapists. Tested by 100+ tech-neck girlies over 12 weeks. Quietly engineered, prettily packaged.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-split__media">
          {%- if section.settings.photo_sebastian != blank -%}
            <img
              src="{{ section.settings.photo_sebastian | image_url: width: 900 }}"
              alt="the pretty fix — How we curate"
              class="about-split__img"
              loading="lazy"
            >
            <p class="about-caption">Three pieces. That's the system.</p>
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="about-photo-placeholder">
              <span>📷 Photo: Product flat lay,<br>detail shot, or workspace</span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 6. WHO WE'RE FOR — dark section ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--dark">
    <div class="container about-truth">
      <span class="about-eyebrow">Who we're for</span>
      <h2 class="about-heading about-heading--light">Built for the<br>Lazy Pretty Girl.</h2>
      <p class="about-body about-body--light">The 27-year-old who works from her bed. Who hates gym lighting. Who buys her own birthday flowers. Who scrolls TikTok with her shoulders rounded forward. Who wants Pilates Princess posture but won't go to Pilates.</p>

      <div class="about-truth__grid">
        <div class="about-truth__card">
          <h3>Passive</h3>
          <p>Every piece works while you live your actual life. No new mornings. No new willpower.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-truth__card about-truth__card--highlight">
          <h3>Permission</h3>
          <p>Rest is the work. Lazy is not a flaw. We don't sell hustle dressed up as wellness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-truth__card">
          <h3>Pretty &amp; Precise</h3>
          <p>The result has to be visible. Engineered with chiropractors. Tested by tech-neck girlies who tried everything else first.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="about-truth__kicker">Soft but knowing.<br>Quiet but engineered.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 7. HOW WE OPERATE ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--beige">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-split about-split--reverse">
        <div class="about-split__media">
          {%- if section.settings.photo_leather != blank -%}
            <img
              src="{{ section.settings.photo_leather | image_url: width: 900 }}"
              alt="the pretty fix — How we operate"
              class="about-split__img"
              loading="lazy"
            >
            <p class="about-caption">Soft service. Real engineering.</p>
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="about-photo-placeholder">
              <span>📷 Photo: Packaging, shipping,<br>or behind-the-scenes detail</span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
        <div class="about-split__text">
          <span class="about-eyebrow about-eyebrow--dark">How we operate</span>
          <h2 class="about-heading">Free Shipping.<br>30-Day Returns.</h2>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>Free US shipping</strong> on every order — no minimums, no games. Orders ship within 1–3 business days and typically arrive in 5–7.</p>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>30-day try-it window</strong>. If your tech neck doesn't budge, send it back. One email, one reply, no runaround.</p>
          <p class="about-body"><strong>Real support</strong>. A person reads every message that comes into <a href="mailto:hello@theprettyfix.com">hello@theprettyfix.com</a>, usually within 24 hours on business days. If we made a mistake, we own it and make it right.</p>
          <p class="about-body">That's the whole model: passive products, clean experience, soft service. Nothing more complicated than that.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── 8. CLOSING ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-closing">
    {%- if section.settings.photo_closing != blank -%}
      <img
        src="{{ section.settings.photo_closing | image_url: width: 2400 }}"
        alt="the pretty fix — Built to endure"
        class="about-closing__img"
        loading="lazy"
      >
    {%- else -%}
      <div class="about-closing__placeholder">[ Photo: Wide brand visual — lifestyle, product, or landscape ]</div>
    {%- endif -%}
    <div class="about-closing__overlay">
      <p class="about-closing__tagline">Rest is the work.</p>
      <p class="about-closing__body">the pretty fix is a small team obsessed with the details — the engineering, the packaging, the soft service. We're building the brand we wanted to find when we typed "tech neck pillow" into TikTok at 11pm and didn't find anything that didn't feel like a hospital.</p>
      <p class="about-closing__sig">— The Pretty Fix Team</p>
      <a href="/collections/all" class="btn about-closing__btn">Shop the System</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<style>
/* ── About page base ── */
.page-about { color: var(--color-text); }

/* Hero */
.about-hero {
  position: relative;
  height: 40vh;
  min-height: 280px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.about-hero__img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  object-position: center;
}
.about-hero__placeholder {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: #2a2a2a;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.about-hero__overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 2rem;
}
.about-hero__title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
  color: #fff;
  margin: 0.5rem 0;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  font-weight: 400;
}
.about-hero__sub {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  margin: 0;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* Eyebrow label */
.about-eyebrow {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.about-eyebrow--dark {
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
}

/* Sections */
.about-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
.about-section--white { background: #fff; }
.about-section--beige { background: #f5f0ea; }
.about-section--dark { background: #111; color: #fff; }

/* Split layout */
.about-split {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: center;
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.about-split--reverse { direction: rtl; }
.about-split--reverse > * { direction: ltr; }

/* Text */
.about-heading {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}
.about-heading--light { color: #fff; }
.about-body {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.about-body--light { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
.about-quote {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--color-text);
  margin: 2rem 0 0;
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--color-text);
}

/* Photo */
.about-split__img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 520px;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
}
.about-photo-placeholder {
  width: 100%;
  height: 520px;
  background: #e8e0d6;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  color: #999;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  border: 2px dashed #ccc;
}
.about-caption {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

/* Stats bar */
.about-stats {
  background: #1a1a1a;
  padding: 3rem 0;
}
.about-stats__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}
.about-stat { padding: 1rem 2rem; }
.about-stat--divider { border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
.about-stat__num {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  color: #fff;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.about-stat__label {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  margin-top: 0.4rem;
}

/* Truth section */
.about-truth { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
.about-truth__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin: 3rem 0;
  text-align: left;
}
.about-truth__card {
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.about-truth__card h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.about-truth__card p {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  margin: 0;
}
.about-truth__card--highlight {
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
}
.about-truth__card--highlight h3 { color: #fff; }
.about-truth__card--highlight p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
.about-truth__kicker {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}

/* Closing */
.about-closing {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 600px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.about-closing__img {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}
.about-closing__placeholder {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: #1a1a1a;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
}
.about-closing__overlay {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  padding: 4rem 3rem;
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.about-closing__tagline {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
  color: #fff;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}
.about-closing__body {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.about-closing__sig {
  font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.about-closing__btn {
  background: #fff;
  color: #111;
  border-color: #fff;
}
.about-closing__btn:hover {
  background: transparent;
  color: #fff;
}

/* ── Mobile ── */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .about-split {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
  .about-split--reverse { direction: ltr; }
  .about-split__img,
  .about-photo-placeholder { height: 320px; }
  .about-stats__grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .about-stat--divider:nth-child(3) { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
  .about-stat--divider:nth-child(4) { border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
  .about-truth__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .about-closing__overlay { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
}
</style>

